     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Generated Narrative: ServiceRequest</b><a name=\"RadiotherapyTreatmentPlan-352-1479\"> </a></p><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Resource ServiceRequest &quot;RadiotherapyTreatmentPlan-352-1479&quot; Version &quot;4056916&quot; Updated &quot;2023-08-21 18:04:47+0200&quot; </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profiles: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/codex-radiation-therapy/STU1/StructureDefinition-codexrt-radiotherapy-treatment-plan.html\">Radiotherapy Treatment Plan</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-RadiotherapyTreatmentPlan.html\">Radiotherapy Treatment Plan</a></p></div><blockquote><p><b>Radiotherapy Modality And Technique Extension</b></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/mcode/STU2.1/StructureDefinition-mcode-radiotherapy-modality.html\">Radiotherapy Modality Extension</a></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: External beam radiation therapy using photons (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#1156506007)</span></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/mcode/STU2.1/StructureDefinition-mcode-radiotherapy-technique.html\">Radiotherapy Technique Extension</a></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: Two dimensional external beam radiation therapy (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#1156526006)</span></p></blockquote><p><b>Number of Planned Fractions</b>: 25</p><blockquote><p><b>Dose Planned to Volume</b></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>volume</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: <a href=\"BodyStructure/BodyStructure-PV-774\">BodyStructure/BodyStructure-PV-774: PTVp</a></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>fractionDose</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: 200.0 cGy<span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow\"> (Details: UCUM code cGy = 'cGy')</span></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>totalDose</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: 5000.0 cGy<span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow\"> (Details: UCUM code cGy = 'cGy')</span></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/codex-radiation-therapy/STU1/StructureDefinition-codexrt-radiotherapy-primary-plan-dose.html\">Primary Plan Dose</a></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: true</p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/codex-radiation-therapy/STU1/StructureDefinition-codexrt-radiotherapy-point-dose.html\">Point Dose</a></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: false</p></blockquote><p><b>identifier</b>: id: Plan_PTVp (use: USUAL), id: 1479 (use: OFFICIAL)</p><p><b>basedOn</b>: </p><ul><li><a href=\"ServiceRequest/RadiotherapyPhasePrescription-352-57\">ServiceRequest/RadiotherapyPhasePrescription-352-57: RxTemp1</a></li><li><a href=\"ServiceRequest/RadiotherapyPlannedPhase-352-57\">ServiceRequest/RadiotherapyPlannedPhase-352-57: RxTemp1</a></li><li><a href=\"ServiceRequest-RadiotherapyPlannedCourse-352-634.html\">ServiceRequest/RadiotherapyPlannedCourse-352-634: C1_Both_Breast</a></li></ul><p><b>status</b>: active</p><p><b>intent</b>: filler-order</p><p><b>category</b>: Radiation oncology AND/OR radiotherapy <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#108290001)</span></p><p><b>code</b>: Radiotherapy treatment plan (regime/therapy) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#1255724003)</span></p><p><b>subject</b>: <a href=\"Patient-Patient-352.html\">Patient/Patient-352: Sister-22B, Jane</a> &quot; SISTER-22B&quot;</p></div>"
